{"tid":1816584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉九龍塘站擲汽油彈4人被控串謀縱火3人准保釋","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T12:15:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9c5e9f53180596f3324801bd05de67c0121463","tid":1816584,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"去年10月12日港鐵九龍塘站有兩部入閘機疑遭人投擲汽油彈縱火破壞，經過警員深入調查，昨晨拘捕5名男子，並在其中一名26歲送貨員的家中疑檢獲汽槍、汽油彈、鎚仔等物件，當中4人今午被帶往九龍城裁判法院應訊。送貨員保釋申請被拒，另外3被告則獲准分別以1萬及10萬現保釋外出，每周須到警署報到3次，但毋須守宵禁令及禁足令。案件押後至3月2日以待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n4被告依次為曾裕生（26歲，送貨員）、黃漢偉（30歲，Party Room店東）、鄭偉森（33歲，自僱人士）及王錦發（40歲，地盤工人），4人被控一項串謀縱火罪，他們被指於2019年10月12日在九龍塘G1出口，無合法辯解而用火損壞屬於香港鐵路有限公司的兩部閘機。曾裕生另被控管有攻擊性武器、管有仿製火器及管有適合作非法用途的工具，被指於1月7日在其住所管有2把摺刀、5個汽油彈、2支氣槍、5支撬筆及3個鎚仔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至3月2日，以待化驗在曾裕生家中所撿取的懷疑汽油彈液體及粉末、化驗涉案氣槍、翻查被告手機的通訊記錄，及較對被告的指模等。控方指稱，案發當日下午2時許，九龍塘站的兩部入閘起火，消防其後發覺火警有可疑，警方於閉路電視片段首先見到一名較瘦削男子在閘機放下汽油彈，未幾一名較略胖的男子點燃該汽油彈。而兩男子亦在事發前後，曾由兩架車接送。<br />\n<br />\n由於案情嚴重，控方反對被告保釋外出，4人同有保釋申請，被告王錦發的代表大律師投訴，被告曾遭警員威嚇，若不交出手機「會搞你老婆仔女」。最終黃漢偉獲准以10萬元保釋外出，鄭、王兩人則准以1萬元外出候訊，3人同不可離港及每周到警署報到3次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4023858/2020-01-08/news-%E6%B6%89%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88+4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB3%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4023858%2F2020-01-08%2Fnews-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%2B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d58b8523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4023858/2020-01-08/news-%E6%B6%89%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88+4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB3%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"dac18023766281cf2807d144db1e47fcc1486c5c","tid":1816584,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55954c7303f85d6adc415aa3835c13c15b887376","tid":1816584,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0ad4e0f5b55dafe1bba4dc53813f379cab102f","tid":1816584,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2479eca8821bee749968ad34700a699647b88f78","tid":1816584,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc378fa8497d759713f4686a3fafeb96835f363","tid":1816584,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ff9f8dd9c1f5b2789c7667ae0f65f877f819d3","tid":1816584,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:25:06.000Z","msg":"點跟？CCTV？"},{"pid":"19c492bd84cb6e7c53bedcec7c3a5c2019203b0e","tid":1816584,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:25:07.000Z","msg":"<im